  "msg_sustainable_development3":
      "\r\nSustainable Development Goal 15 (SDG 15), \"Life on Land,\" aims to protect, restore, and promote sustainable use of terrestrial ecosystems. In 2024, technology plays a critical role in achieving the objectives of SDG 15 by providing innovative solutions to address challenges related to biodiversity conservation, deforestation, and sustainable land management.\r\n\r\n",
