      "1. [Convention on Biological Diversity (CBD)](https://www.cbd.int/)\r\n2. [IUCN Red List of Threatened Species](https://www.iucnredlist.org/)\r\n3. [Global Biodiversity Outlook 5](https://www.cbd.int/gbo5/)\r\n\r\nIncorporating biodiversity conservation into sustainable development practices is crucial for achieving the objectives of SDG 15 and ensuring a resilient and thriving planet for future generations.",
